text: Claes-Göran Hederström, (20 October 1945 – 8 November 2022) was a Swedish singer. He made his musical debut at SVT in 1967. He represented Sweden in the Eurovision Song Contest 1968 with the song Det börjar verka kärlek, banne mej. The song ended up coming 5th. ==Death== Hederström died on 8 November 2022, at the age of 77. == References == ==Other websites== * claesgoranhederstrom.com Category:1945 births Category:Swedish singers Category:Living people
